      "description": "Bench-test records for N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were retrieved from the sponsor's device-history archive and from a second independent laboratory. Specimen geometry, material certificates, and test-machine calibration logs were reviewed post hoc to confirm ASTM F1717 compliance. FEA predictions were then compared against the archived force-displacement curves. The activity comprehensively characterises the experimental population and provides a statistically meaningful comparison basis, yielding E/uval values well below 1.96 for all three QoIs.",
